com.orchestranetworks.ui.action

Class DisplayMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orchestranetworks.ui.action.DisplayMode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DisplayMode.ModalCustom, DisplayMode.ModalMedium, DisplayMode.Workspace

    public abstract class DisplayMode
extends Object
    Defines how a toolbar action has to be displayed on launch. Possible values are:
    • Workspace(), obtained using workspace()
    • ModalMedium(resizable), obtained using modalMedium(boolean)
    • ModalCustom(width, height, resizable), obtained using modalCustom(int, int, boolean)
    Since:
    5.9.0
    See Also:
    WebComponentAction.setDisplayMode(DisplayMode)
